data.2getupdatedroutespath#2.getUpdatedRoutes:
Signature:
getUpdatedRoutesPath(lastRunTimeStamp: number, lookupPatterns: string[], ignorePattern: string[]): string[]
Description:Detects routes that have been modified since the last submission, using specified inclusion and exclusion patterns.Example:
const updatedRoutes = utilities.getUpdatedRoutesPath(lastRunTimeStamp, ['**/*.html'], ['node_modules/**']);
console.log(updatedRoutes);

